settings.description: Fed up with Mario beating them up time and time again, all of the enemies turn giganto! Use the starman to blast your way through these larger-than-life foes.
My 1st level i guess, have fun

Back-trek your way to secrets, special coins, and warps!

--A redesign of Back-Tracking Bonanza--

Ah, the wonders of the underground desert...

--Intended with any character, its basically the same experience)--

A gaping scenery with secrets all around!

-Intended to be played with any character--
--Remake of Warping Mania--
Hammers are practically everywhere, attacking from all sides! Make sure to avoid them!

The game is glitching, and I haven't been able to cancel it out. Thus, I had to rename the level.

In this field, Fireflowers grow naturally out of the floor, how convenient!
